    <iof-av:adaptedFrom rdf:resource="http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/PATO_0001607"/>
    <iof-av:naturalLanguageDefinition xml:lang="en-US">Tangled quality inhering in a bearer by virtue of the bearer's being not possible to unravel</iof-av:naturalLanguageDefinition>
    <iof-av:isPrimitive rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#boolean">true</iof-av:isPrimitive>
    <iof-av:primitiveRationale xml:lang="en-US">Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'matted' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'tangled'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions. The definition is adapted from: http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/PATO_0001607.</iof-av:primitiveRationale>
