    <rdfs:label xml:lang="de">olivgrün</rdfs:label>
    <iof-av:adaptedFrom rdf:resource="http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/PATO_0002773"/>
    <iof-av:naturalLanguageDefinition xml:lang="en-US">Brown-green color hue associated with green olives, often dull</iof-av:naturalLanguageDefinition>
    <iof-av:isPrimitive rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#boolean">true</iof-av:isPrimitive>
    <iof-av:primitiveRationale xml:lang="en-US">Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'olive' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'brown green'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions. The definition is adapted from: http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/PATO_0002773.</iof-av:primitiveRationale>
    <iof-av:firstOrderLogicAxiom xml:lang="en-US">BrownGreen(x) ← Olive(x)</iof-av:firstOrderLogicAxiom>
    <iof-av:semiFormalNaturalLanguageAxiom xml:lang="en-US">if x is a &apos;olive&apos; then x is a &apos;brown green&apos;</iof-av:semiFormalNaturalLanguageAxiom>
