    <iof-av:naturalLanguageDefinition xml:lang="en-US">Structural quality characterized by wood-like appearance or texture</iof-av:naturalLanguageDefinition>
    <iof-av:isPrimitive rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#boolean">true</iof-av:isPrimitive>
    <iof-av:primitiveRationale xml:lang="en-US">Necessary and sufficient conditions for 'ligneous' have not yet been formalized. The term is defined as a specific subtype of 'structure'. Distinguishing criteria are domain-specific and depend on measurement conventions or source terminology not yet expressed as OWL restrictions. The definition is adapted from: http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/PATO_0002348.</iof-av:primitiveRationale>
