    <iof-av:firstOrderLogicAxiom xml:lang="en-US">Flattened(x) ← LaterallyCompressed(x)</iof-av:firstOrderLogicAxiom>
    <iof-av:semiFormalNaturalLanguageAxiom xml:lang="en-US">if x is a &apos;laterally compressed&apos; then x is a &apos;flattened&apos;</iof-av:semiFormalNaturalLanguageAxiom>
